ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectOrder repealing order P.C. 2011-815 and establishing payments for Designated Barley ** August 2011 - July 2012 INITIAL PAYMENTS **
PrecisOrder repealing order P.C. 2011-815 and approving sums fixed by the Canadian Wheat Board to establish the initial payments for grades other than the base grade of DESIGNATED BARLEY for the pool period commencing on August 1, 2011 and ending on July 31, 2012.
